        "html": "<div class=\"w-full h-full flex flex-col justify-between p-12\" style=\"position: relative;\">\n\n  <!-- Hero SVG ambient background — centered round-trip loop, opacity 0.3 -->\n  <div style=\"position: absolute; inset: 0; opacity: 0.3; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; overflow: hidden; pointer-events: none;\">\n    <img data-slot=\"hero_round_trip_loop\" src=\"svgs/slide_1_hero_round_trip_loop.svg\" class=\"shuttleslide-svg-placeholder\" data-image-type=\"hero\" data-description=\"Abstract hero visual: a large glowing circular loop/arrow diagram in primary blue and cyan, symbolizing bidirectional round-trip conversion. The loop is composed of two opposing curved arrows (PPTX→HTML and HTML→PPTX) meeting at a central diamond node labeled 'Metadata Vault'. Subtle orbital data particles dot the background. Glassmorphism glow effects.\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;\" />\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- TITLE — top-left quadrant -->\n  <div class=\"flex flex-col items-start\" style=\"position: relative; z-index: 2; margin-top: 36px;\">\n    <h1 style=\"font-size: 56px; color: {{theme.title_color}}; font-family: {{theme.font_title}}, sans-serif; font-weight: 700; line-height: 1.15; max-width: 680px; margin: 0; letter-spacing: -0.5px;\">\n      Shuttleslide:<br/>The Round-Trip Story\n    </h1>\n    <div style=\"width: 140px; height: 4px; background: linear-gradient(90deg, {{theme.primary_color}} 0%, {{theme.accent_color}} 100%); margin-top: 16px; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: 0 0 20px {{theme.primary_rgba:0.5}};\"></div>\n    <p style=\"font-size: 20px; color: rgba(232,237,245,0.7); font-family: {{theme.font_body}}, sans-serif; max-width: 580px; margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 0; line-height: 1.5;\">\n      Lossless bidirectional PPTX↔HTML conversion with metadata preservation — enabling true round-trip editing.\n    </p>\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- Spacer — ambient SVG fills this area naturally -->\n  <div style=\"flex: 1;\"></div>\n\n  <!-- STAT BADGES — three glassmorphism callout cards -->\n  <div class=\"flex items-center gap-6\" style=\"position: relative; z-index: 2; margin-bottom: 8px;\">\n    \n    <div class=\"card\" style=\"background: rgba(255,255,255,0.07); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12); border-radius: 14px; padding: 14px 26px;\">\n      <div class=\"flex items-center gap-3\">\n        <i class=\"material-icons\" style=\"font-size: 30px; color: {{theme.accent_color}};\">sync_alt</i>\n        <span style=\"font-size: 22px; color: {{theme.title_color}}; font-family: {{theme.font_title}}, sans-serif; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.3px;\">Bidirectional</span>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"card\" style=\"background: rgba(255,255,255,0.07); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12); border-radius: 14px; padding: 14px 26px;\">\n      <div class=\"flex items-center gap-3\">\n        <i class=\"material-icons\" style=\"font-size: 30px; color: {{theme.accent_color}};\">verified</i>\n        <span style=\"font-size: 22px; color: {{theme.title_color}}; font-family: {{theme.font_title}}, sans-serif; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.3px;\">Metadata-Preserving</span>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"card\" style=\"background: rgba(255,255,255,0.07); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12); border-radius: 14px; padding: 14px 26px;\">\n      <div class=\"flex items-center gap-3\">\n        <i class=\"material-icons\" style=\"font-size: 30px; color: {{theme.accent_color}};\">check_circle</i>\n        <span style=\"font-size: 22px; color: {{theme.title_color}}; font-family: {{theme.font_title}}, sans-serif; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.3px;\">Lossless</span>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- FOOTER — page number left, logo watermark right -->\n  <div class=\"flex items-center justify-between\" style=\"position: relative; z-index: 2; margin-top: 16px;\">\n    <span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgba(232,237,245,0.35); font-family: {{theme.font_body}}, sans-serif;\">01 / 06</span>\n    <span style=\"font-size: 13px; color: rgba(232,237,245,0.25); font-family: {{theme.font_body}}, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 3px; text-transform: uppercase;\">Shuttleslide</span>\n  </div>\n\n</div>"
      }
    },
