      "elements": [],
      "slots": {
        "html": "<div class=\"w-full h-full flex flex-col justify-between\" style=\"background-color: {{theme.bg_color}}; position: relative;\">\n\n  <!-- Top accent bar -->\n  <div style=\"position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 4px; background: linear-gradient(90deg, {{theme.primary_color}} 0%, {{theme.accent_color}} 100%);\"></div>\n\n  <!-- Decorative blur glow (top-right) -->\n  <div style=\"position: absolute; top: -120px; right: -80px; width: 360px; height: 360px; border-radius: 9999px; background-color: {{theme.primary_color}}; opacity: 0.10; filter: blur(80px);\"></div>\n\n  <!-- Decorative blur glow (bottom-left) -->\n  <div style=\"position: absolute; bottom: -100px; left: -60px; width: 280px; height: 280px; border-radius: 9999px; background-color: {{theme.accent_color}}; opacity: 0.08; filter: blur(70px);\"></div>\n\n  <!-- Main glassmorphism card -->\n  <div style=\"flex: 1; margin: 36px 24px 0 24px; border-radius: 20px; background-color: {{theme.primary_rgba:0.06}}; border: 1px solid {{theme.primary_rgba:0.15}}; padding: 36px 32px; display: flex; flex-direction: row; gap: 32px;\">\n\n    <!-- Left column: Title + Numbered Steps -->\n    <div style=\"width: 35%; min-width: 380px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: flex-start;\">\n\n      <!-- Title -->\n      <h1 style=\"font-size: 36px; font-weight: 700; color: {{theme.title_color}}; font-family: {{theme.font_title}}, sans-serif; line-height: 1.15; margin: 0 0 6px 0;\">\n        PPTX → HTML:\n      </h1>\n      <h1 style=\"font-size: 36px; font-weight: 700; color: {{theme.title_color}}; font-family: {{theme.font_title}}, sans-serif; line-height: 1.15; margin: 0 0 24px 0;\">\n        Forward Conversion Pipeline\n      </h1>\n\n      <!-- Accent divider below title -->\n      <div style=\"width: 80px; height: 3px; background: linear-gradient(90deg, {{theme.primary_color}}, {{theme.accent_color}}); border-radius: 2px; margin-bottom: 28px;\"></div>\n\n      <!-- Numbered Steps -->\n      <div class=\"flex flex-col\" style=\"gap: 18px;\">\n\n        <!-- Step 01 -->\n        <div class=\"flex items-start gap-4\" style=\"display: flex; gap: 14px;\">\n          <div style=\"width: 40px; height: 40px; min-width: 40px; border-radius: 9999px; background-color: {{theme.accent_color}}; color: #0B0F1A; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; font-family: {{theme.font_title}}, sans-serif; box-shadow: 0 0 12px {{theme.accent_rgba:0.4}};\">01</div>\n          <div>\n            <p style=\"font-size: 15px; color: {{theme.text_color}}; font-family: {{theme.font_body}}, sans-serif; line-height: 1.55; margin: 0;\">\n              Shuttleslide unzips the PPTX container (a ZIP archive) and parses its XML parts — including slide XML, theme XML, slideLayout XML, and shared relationships — to reconstruct the full presentation tree.\n            </p>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n\n        <!-- Step 02 -->\n        <div class=\"flex items-start gap-4\" style=\"display: flex; gap: 14px;\">\n          <div style=\"width: 40px; height: 40px; min-width: 40px; border-radius: 9999px; background-color: {{theme.accent_color}}; color: #0B0F1A; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; font-family: {{theme.font_title}}, sans-serif; box-shadow: 0 0 12px {{theme.accent_rgba:0.4}};\">02</div>\n          <div>\n            <p style=\"font-size: 15px; color: {{theme.text_color}}; font-family: {{theme.font_body}}, sans-serif; line-height: 1.55; margin: 0;\">\n              Each parsed element's formatting attributes (font family, size, color, paragraph alignment, table borders, fill styles) are resolved through the master→layout→slide style hierarchy and mapped into equivalent CSS properties with <code style=\"color: {{theme.accent_color}}; font-size: 14px; background-color: {{theme.primary_rgba:0.15}}; padding: 1px 6px; border-radius: 4px;\">data-*</code> attributes preserving the original PPTX identifiers.\n            </p>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n\n        <!-- Step 03 -->\n        <div class=\"flex items-start gap-4\" style=\"display: flex; gap: 14px;\">\n          <div style=\"width: 40px; height: 40px; min-width: 40px; border-radius: 9999px; background-color: {{theme.accent_color}}; color: #0B0F1A; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; font-family: {{theme.font_title}}, sans-serif; box-shadow: 0 0 12px {{theme.accent_rgba:0.4}};\">03</div>\n          <div>\n            <p style=\"font-size: 15px; color: {{theme.text_color}}; font-family: {{theme.font_body}}, sans-serif; line-height: 1.55; margin: 0;\">\n              The engine emits semantic HTML5 documents where every shape, text run, table cell, and image is tagged with its original PPTX structure metadata, enabling exact round-trip reconstruction back to XML.\n            </p>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- Right column: Flowchart SVG -->\n    <div style=\"flex: 1; min-width: 720px; border-radius: 14px; background-color: {{theme.primary_rgba:0.04}}; border: 1px solid {{theme.primary_rgba:0.12}}; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; padding: 16px;\">\n      <div style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%;\">\n        <img data-slot=\"forward_pipeline_flowchart\" src=\"svgs/slide_2_forward_pipeline_flowchart.svg\" class=\"shuttleslide-svg-placeholder\" data-image-type=\"flowchart\" data-description=\"Pipeline flowchart showing: PPTX container (ZIP) → XML Parsing (slide.xml, theme.xml, slideLayout.xml) → Style Resolution (master→layout→slide CSS mapping) → Semantic HTML5 Emission with data-* metadata annotations. Boxes connected by directional arrows, styled in primary_color and accent_color on dark background.\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;\" />\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- Footer -->\n  <div class=\"flex flex-row items-center justify-between\" style=\"display: flex; flex-direction: row; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; padding: 14px 32px 16px 32px;\">\n    <span style=\"font-size: 13px; color: rgba(232,237,245,0.35); font-family: {{theme.font_body}}, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;\">02 / 06</span>\n    <span style=\"font-size: 12px; color: rgba(232,237,245,0.25); font-family: {{theme.font_body}}, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 3px; font-weight: 500;\">SHUTTLESLIDE</span>\n  </div>\n\n</div>"
      }
    },
    {
      "layout": "free_form",
      "background": null,
      "elements": [],
      "slots": {
        "background": {
          "strategy": "solid"
        },
        "html": "<div class=\"w-full h-full flex flex-col justify-between p-12\" style=\"background-color: {{theme.bg_color}};\">\n\n  <!-- Top section: accent bar + title + pipeline label -->\n  <div class=\"flex flex-col\" style=\"flex-shrink: 0;\">\n    <!-- Glowing accent bar -->\n    <div style=\"width: 100%; height: 4px; background: linear-gradient(90deg, {{theme.primary_color}} 0%, {{theme.accent_color}} 100%); border-radius: 2px; margin-bottom: 16px;\"></div>\n\n    <!-- Title row with arrow icon -->\n    <div class=\"flex items-center gap-3\" style=\"margin-bottom: 20px;\">\n      <h1 style=\"font-size: 36px; font-family: {{theme.font_title}}, sans-serif; color: {{theme.title_color}}; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: -0.5px; margin: 0; line-height: 1.2;\">HTML → PPTX: Reverse Conversion Pipeline</h1>\n      <i class=\"material-icons\" style=\"font-size: 36px; color: {{theme.accent_color}}; margin-top: 4px;\">arrow_forward</i>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- Pipeline Step label -->\n    <div style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px;\">\n      <span style=\"font-size: 13px; font-family: {{theme.font_body}}, sans-serif; color: #8899B0; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1.5px; font-weight: 500;\">Pipeline Step</span>\n      <div style=\"flex: 1; max-width: 120px; height: 1px; background: linear-gradient(90deg, {{theme.accent_rgba:0.4}} 0%, transparent 100%);\"></div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- Steps area with connecting lines -->\n  <div class=\"flex flex-col\" style=\"flex: 1; justify-content: center; gap: 0; max-width: 1000px; margin: 0 auto; width: 100%;\">\n\n    <!-- Step 01 -->\n    <div class=\"card\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.06); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08); border-radius: 14px; padding: 20px 24px; display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 20px; box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.25);\">\n      <div style=\"width: 48px; height: 48px; border-radius: 9999px; background-color: {{theme.accent_color}}; color: #0B0F1A; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 20px; font-family: {{theme.font_title}}, sans-serif; font-weight: 700; flex-shrink: 0;\">01</div>\n      <div style=\"flex: 1;\">\n        <p style=\"font-size: 17px; font-family: {{theme.font_body}}, sans-serif; color: {{theme.text_color}}; margin: 0; line-height: 1.5;\">The reverse pipeline parses the HTML document tree and maps semantic elements (sections, headings, paragraphs, lists) back to PowerPoint's native shape and text hierarchy (p:sp, a:p, a:r).</p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- Dashed connecting line -->\n    <div style=\"width: 2px; height: 32px; margin-left: 48px; border-left: 2px dashed {{theme.accent_color}}; opacity: 0.5; margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0;\"></div>\n\n    <!-- Step 02 -->\n    <div class=\"card\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.06); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08); border-radius: 14px; padding: 20px 24px; display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 20px; box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.25);\">\n      <div style=\"width: 48px; height: 48px; border-radius: 9999px; background-color: {{theme.accent_color}}; color: #0B0F1A; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 20px; font-family: {{theme.font_title}}, sans-serif; font-weight: 700; flex-shrink: 0;\">02</div>\n      <div style=\"flex: 1;\">\n        <p style=\"font-size: 17px; font-family: {{theme.font_body}}, sans-serif; color: {{theme.text_color}}; margin: 0; line-height: 1.5;\">Inline formatting encoded as CSS properties (font-weight, font-style, color, font-size) is translated to PowerPoint XML run-level properties (a:rPr), preserving bold, italic, hyperlinks, and exact font metrics.</p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- Dashed connecting line -->\n    <div style=\"width: 2px; height: 32px; margin-left: 48px; border-left: 2px dashed {{theme.accent_color}}; opacity: 0.5; margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0;\"></div>\n\n    <!-- Step 03 -->\n    <div class=\"card\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.06); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08); border-radius: 14px; padding: 20px 24px; display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 20px; box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.25);\">\n      <div style=\"width: 48px; height: 48px; border-radius: 9999px; background-color: {{theme.accent_color}}; color: #0B0F1A; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 20px; font-family: {{theme.font_title}}, sans-serif; font-weight: 700; flex-shrink: 0;\">03</div>\n      <div style=\"flex: 1;\">\n        <p style=\"font-size: 17px; font-family: {{theme.font_body}}, sans-serif; color: {{theme.text_color}}; margin: 0; line-height: 1.5;\">Custom metadata stored as data attributes in the HTML — including slide dimensions, layout references, slide numbers, and custom XML parts — is extracted and reinjected into the PPTX package's document properties and slide relationships.</p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- Dashed connecting line -->\n    <div style=\"width: 2px; height: 32px; margin-left: 48px; border-left: 2px dashed {{theme.accent_color}}; opacity: 0.5; margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0;\"></div>\n\n    <!-- Step 04 -->\n    <div class=\"card\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.06); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08); border-radius: 14px; padding: 20px 24px; display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 20px; box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.25);\">\n      <div style=\"width: 48px; height: 48px; border-radius: 9999px; background-color: {{theme.accent_color}}; color: #0B0F1A; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 20px; font-family: {{theme.font_title}}, sans-serif; font-weight: 700; flex-shrink: 0;\">04</div>\n      <div style=\"flex: 1;\">\n        <p style=\"font-size: 17px; font-family: {{theme.font_body}}, sans-serif; color: {{theme.text_color}}; margin: 0; line-height: 1.5;\">The converter reconstructs the full PresentationML structure (slide masters, layouts, theme elements, and slide-level relationships), ensuring the output .pptx file opens natively in PowerPoint without compatibility issues.</p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- Footer: page number left, Shuttleslide watermark right -->\n  <div class=\"flex items-center justify-between\" style=\"flex-shrink: 0; padding-top: 12px; margin-top: 8px; border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);\">\n    <span style=\"font-size: 12px; font-family: {{theme.font_body}}, sans-serif; color: #5A6B83; letter-spacing: 0.5px;\">03 / 06</span>\n    <div class=\"flex items-center gap-2\">\n      <span style=\"font-size: 13px; font-family: {{theme.font_body}}, sans-serif; color: #5A6B83; letter-spacing: 1px; font-weight: 500;\">Shuttleslide</span>\n      <i class=\"material-icons\" style=\"font-size: 16px; color: #5A6B83;\">rocket_launch</i>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n</div>"
      }
    },
