        "html": "<div class=\"w-full h-full flex flex-col\" style=\"overflow: hidden;\">\n\n  <!-- Top glowing accent bar -->\n  <div style=\"width: 100%; height: 4px; background: linear-gradient(90deg, {{theme.primary_color}} 0%, {{theme.accent_color}} 100%); box-shadow: 0 0 12px {{theme.primary_rgba:0.4}};\"></div>\n\n  <!-- Main content area -->\n  <div class=\"flex flex-col justify-between\" style=\"flex: 1; padding: 24px 40px 18px 40px;\">\n\n    <!-- Title row -->\n    <div style=\"margin-bottom: 14px;\">\n      <h2 style=\"font-size: 30px; font-weight: 700; color: {{theme.title_color}}; font-family: {{theme.font_title}}, sans-serif; margin: 0; letter-spacing: -0.3px;\">\n        Metadata Preservation: What Survives the Trip\n      </h2>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- Body: left cards + right diagram -->\n    <div class=\"flex flex-row\" style=\"flex: 1; gap: 24px;\">\n\n      <!-- LEFT HALF (45%): 2×2 glassmorphism card grid -->\n      <div style=\"width: 45%; display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 12px; align-content: start;\">\n\n        <!-- Card 1: Styles -->\n        <div style=\"background-color: {{theme.primary_rgba:0.06}}; border: 1px solid {{theme.primary_rgba:0.15}}; border-radius: 12px; padding: 14px 12px 12px 12px;\">\n          <div class=\"flex items-center gap-2\" style=\"margin-bottom: 6px;\">\n            <i class=\"material-icons\" style=\"font-size: 20px; color: {{theme.accent_color}};\">text_fields</i>\n            <h3 style=\"font-size: 17px; font-weight: 600; color: {{theme.title_color}}; font-family: {{theme.font_title}}, sans-serif; margin: 0;\">Styles</h3>\n          </div>\n          <p style=\"font-size: 12.5px; color: {{theme.text_color}}; line-height: 1.5; margin: 0; opacity: 0.85;\">\n            Font families, sizes, weights, colors — paragraph alignment, spacing, indentation — background fills (solid, gradient, pattern) — fully preserved bidirectionally.\n          </p>\n        </div>\n\n        <!-- Card 2: Layout -->\n        <div style=\"background-color: {{theme.primary_rgba:0.06}}; border: 1px solid {{theme.primary_rgba:0.15}}; border-radius: 12px; padding: 14px 12px 12px 12px;\">\n          <div class=\"flex items-center gap-2\" style=\"margin-bottom: 6px;\">\n            <i class=\"material-icons\" style=\"font-size: 20px; color: {{theme.accent_color}};\">view_quilt</i>\n            <h3 style=\"font-size: 17px; font-weight: 600; color: {{theme.title_color}}; font-family: {{theme.font_title}}, sans-serif; margin: 0;\">Layout</h3>\n          </div>\n          <p style=\"font-size: 12.5px; color: {{theme.text_color}}; line-height: 1.5; margin: 0; opacity: 0.85;\">\n            Slide dimensions, placeholder positions and sizes, hierarchical slide master/layout relationships — faithfully converted in both directions.\n          </p>\n        </div>\n\n        <!-- Card 3: Properties -->\n        <div style=\"background-color: {{theme.primary_rgba:0.06}}; border: 1px solid {{theme.primary_rgba:0.15}}; border-radius: 12px; padding: 14px 12px 12px 12px;\">\n          <div class=\"flex items-center gap-2\" style=\"margin-bottom: 6px;\">\n            <i class=\"material-icons\" style=\"font-size: 20px; color: {{theme.accent_color}};\">description</i>\n            <h3 style=\"font-size: 17px; font-weight: 600; color: {{theme.title_color}}; font-family: {{theme.font_title}}, sans-serif; margin: 0;\">Properties</h3>\n          </div>\n          <p style=\"font-size: 12.5px; color: {{theme.text_color}}; line-height: 1.5; margin: 0; opacity: 0.85;\">\n            Author, title, subject, company, and arbitrary key-value pairs survive intact — along with per-slide speaker notes in both PPTX→HTML and HTML→PPTX.\n          </p>\n        </div>\n\n        <!-- Card 4: Notes -->\n        <div style=\"background-color: {{theme.primary_rgba:0.06}}; border: 1px solid {{theme.primary_rgba:0.15}}; border-radius: 12px; padding: 14px 12px 12px 12px;\">\n          <div class=\"flex items-center gap-2\" style=\"margin-bottom: 6px;\">\n            <i class=\"material-icons\" style=\"font-size: 20px; color: {{theme.accent_color}};\">sticky_note_2</i>\n            <h3 style=\"font-size: 17px; font-weight: 600; color: {{theme.title_color}}; font-family: {{theme.font_title}}, sans-serif; margin: 0;\">Notes</h3>\n          </div>\n          <p style=\"font-size: 12.5px; color: {{theme.text_color}}; line-height: 1.5; margin: 0; opacity: 0.85;\">\n            Speaker notes, table formatting (borders, cell shading, merged cells, alignment), and shape geometry (position, size, rotation, fill/stroke) — preserved down to each individual shape.\n          </p>\n        </div>\n\n      </div>\n\n      <!-- RIGHT HALF (55%): Diagram container -->\n      <div style=\"width: 55%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;\">\n        <div style=\"width: 100%; max-width: 600px; border: 1px solid {{theme.primary_rgba:0.25}}; border-radius: 16px; padding: 14px; background-color: {{theme.primary_rgba:0.04}};\">\n          <img data-slot=\"metadata_diagram\" src=\"svgs/slide_4_metadata_diagram.svg\" class=\"shuttleslide-svg-placeholder\" data-image-type=\"diagram\" data-description=\"A circular Venn-like diagram showing four intersecting metadata domains — Styles, Layout, Properties, Notes — converging at the center labeled 'Shuttleslide Round Trip'.\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; display: block;\" />\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- Footer: page number left, logo right -->\n    <div class=\"flex flex-row justify-between items-center\" style=\"margin-top: 12px; padding-top: 10px; border-top: 1px dashed {{theme.accent_rgba:0.2}};\">\n      <span style=\"font-size: 13px; color: {{theme.text_color}}; opacity: 0.4;\">04 / 06</span>\n      <div class=\"flex items-center gap-2\">\n        <i class=\"material-icons\" style=\"font-size: 16px; color: {{theme.accent_color}}; opacity: 0.6;\">rocket_launch</i>\n        <span style=\"font-size: 13px; co